timeline.bodyText:
@joeygrover The comment and the logic are mismatched here.
should this be:
if(ddState.getLockscreenDismissibility() == null ) {
    isLockscreenDismissible = previousDismissibleState;
} else {
    isLockscreenDismissible = ddState.getLockscreenDismissibility();
}

